message.content: cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.COMM, cs.SY - This paper discusses resource sharing in mmWave cellular networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of networked systems (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), communication (cs.COMM), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, since the paper focuses on the technical and economical aspects of resource sharing in mmWave networks, the most likely sub-categories are cs.NI and cs.IT, followed by cs.MM, cs.COMM, and cs.SY.
